//提权漏洞
var webBug=[
    {'title':'WEB提权'},
    {'introduce':'<p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">提权漏洞 主要包括：<span><br> 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>了解<span>Web</span>应用系统用户级别管理的实现原理<span><br> 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>了解提权漏洞的相关知识<span> <br> 3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>掌握提权漏洞产生的原因（用户级别管理模块中，因身份验证不充分，引发提权漏洞，导致普通用户可获取<span>VIP</span>用户的权限）<span> <br> 4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>掌握提权漏洞的检测方法及利用手段<span><br> 5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>体验并了解提权漏洞造成的危害 掌握提权漏洞的预防措施</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">通过一个实例来分析学习提权漏洞的检测、利用与预防。<span><br> <b>1.</b></span><b>案例分析对<span>WeCenter</span>中存在的垂直提权漏洞进行利用：<span><br> </span></b><span>1</span>）检测是否存在提权漏洞的思路；<span> <br> 2</span>）登录网站，发现漏洞；<span><br> 3</span>）利用漏洞进行提权；<span> <br> 4</span>）如何预防。<span><br> <b>2</b></span><b>．本案例提权中所运用到的工具：</b><span> <br> </span>火狐浏览器及其扩展应用：<span>firebug</span>，用于查看并修改当前的<span>cookie</span>。</span></p><p><br></p>'},
    {'steps':`<p><span>1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">．如何检测提权漏洞</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">首先，我们打开浏览器登录网站</span><span>wandouxia.cn</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，查看在</span><span>cookie</span><span style="font-family:宋体">中是否存在</span><span>uid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">与</span><span>gid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">。若不存在，我们再通过提交表单，尝试寻找是否存在</span><span>uid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span><span>gid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，或是一些其它类似的名称，如</span><span>userid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span><span>username</span><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">当我们找到这些后，若它们不是加密的，则可能存在提权漏洞，我们可以直接修改其值以达到我们的提权目的；如果加密了，还需能够解密再利用该漏洞。</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">．登录教学试验平台，发现漏洞</span></p><p><span>1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）打开浏览器，访问教学试验平台</span><span>wandouxia.cn</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">来到教学实验平台页面后，我们首先需要进行注册一个用户。</span></p><p><span>2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）在教学试验平台中注册需要邀请码。使用之前课程所学习到的知识进行绕过。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">在逻辑上绕过这个邀请码。如图</span><span>1-1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span><span>a</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）（</span><span>b</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）所示。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="832" height="522" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image001.jpg" alt="20160201591503273636.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span><span>a</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）注册界面</span></p><p><span>3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）注册登录之后，我们用户的权限是普通用户。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="683" height="388" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image003.jpg" alt="20160201591526270227.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span><span>b</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）登录后</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>4</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）如图</span><span>1-2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">所示，这里，我们发现了一个</span><span>“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">管理</span><span>”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">的选项。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="601" height="330" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image004.jpg" alt="20160201591541394200.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">发现管理项</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）点击后尝试登录，但发现权限不够无法登陆。如图</span><span>1-3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">所示。</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="392" height="584" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image005.jpg" alt="20160201591546857288.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">无权限访问</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>6</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）我们打开</span><span>firebug</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，发现在</span><span>cookie</span><span style="font-family:宋体">中，出现了两项：</span><span>wid_gid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span><span>wid_uid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">。（具体数值以当时情况为准）如图</span><span>1-4</span><span style="font-family:宋体">所示。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="610" height="282" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image007.jpg" alt="20160201591551816117.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-4 </span><span style="font-family:宋体">在</span><span>cookie</span><span style="font-family:宋体">中发现</span><span>uid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">与</span><span>gid</span></p><p><span>7</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）由于</span><span>gid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">与</span><span>uid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">未进行加密，在此明文显示，故可以认为该网站可能存在提权漏洞，我们可以编辑该参数来检测是否确实存在此漏洞。</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">．利用漏洞进行提权</span></p><p><span>1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）我们进行编辑这两个</span><span>cookie</span><span style="font-family:宋体">的值。如图</span><span>1-5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">所示。</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="571" height="395" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image008.jpg" alt="20160201001605313274.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">编辑</span><span>cookie</span><span style="font-family:宋体">中</span><span>uid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">与</span><span>gid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">值</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）在用户管理模块中，每个用户的权限就保存在</span><span>uid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">与</span><span>gid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">中。这里，我们把它们的内</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">容修改为</span><span>1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">。如图</span><span>1-6</span><span style="font-family:宋体">所示。</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="389" height="338" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image009.jpg" alt="20160201001609708094.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-6</span><span style="font-family:宋体">将</span><span>gid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">中的值更改为</span><span>1</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）我们修改完成后，再次尝试登录。如图</span><span>1-7</span><span style="font-family:宋体">所示。</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="392" height="329" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image010.jpg" alt="20160201001615123483.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-7 </span><span style="font-family:宋体">更改完</span><span>gid</span><span style="font-family:宋体">值后，再次尝试登录</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>4</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）这一次，我们发现我们登录成功，进入管理员后台页面。如图</span><span>1-8</span><span style="font-family:宋体">所示。</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="667" height="398" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image012.jpg" alt="20160201001619620232.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-8</span><span style="font-family:宋体">成功进入后台</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）但虽然现在暂时拥有管理员权限，但我们登录使用的用户还是普通权限，只是我们暂时利用了提权漏洞使自己提权了。所以，我们要将提权进行到底！</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>6</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）我们可以清楚地看到每个用户的一切信息，包括权限等级。我们需要找到用户管理</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">模块，然后找到我们自己创建的那个用户。如图</span><span>1-9</span><span style="font-family:宋体">所示。</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="789" height="267" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image014.jpg" alt="20160201001628792817.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-9 </span><span style="font-family:宋体">进入用户管理界面</span></p><p><span> <hr></span> </p><p><span>7</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）我们可以把自己的权限调整成为</span><span>“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">超级管理员</span><span>”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，然后点击保存设置。如图</span><span>1-10</span><span style="font-family:宋体">所示。</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span><img width="799" height="389" src="img/simulationModule/webBug//clip_image016.jpg" alt="20160201001638875592.jpg"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span>1-10 </span><span style="font-family:宋体">正式提权</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">这样这个用户就成为了这个网站的管理员。以后我们登录，就是以管理员的身份登录了。</span></p><p><br></p>`}
]

